# Board of Directors

SPI is run by its Board of Directors and the officers they select.  All 
current officers are also directors.

SPI directors come from around the world and currently include residents and citizens of Australia, Canada, Germany, the United Kingdom and the United States.

Listed below are the officers, directors and advisors along with their email 
addresses and, where relevant, their registered 
[OFTC](http://www.oftc.net) IRC nicks.

